Bxe5 {The position has settled down and white stands fine here. Black's kingside 
is weakened severely. White has good pieces. The light squared bishop for black 
is suffering. And white has easy play here.} O-O 13. Rh3 {Not taking h5 because 
of Rf5. Rh3 prepares Rg3 with a massive attack.} *

