make accurate moves to equalize.} 6. e5 $1 {An excellent move to prevent e6-e5 
from black.} dxe5 7. Nxe5 Qg5 $5 {White has to play a bit carefully here.} 8. 
Ng4 {Defending g2 and the knight.} f5 9. Qf3 $1 {White attacks c6. And this 
