Ng6 7. h4 h5 {Prevents h5.} 8. e5 {Further limiting black. Taking away f6 and 
e5. As well as weakening d6.} d6 {Played between Adams-Shirov 2003.} 9. exd6 
Qxd6 10. Na3 {White needs to prevent c5-c4. So Na3 stops that idea.} f6 {An 
example line based on the engine.} 11. Nc4 Qd5 12. Ne3 Qd7 13. d3 Nf4 14. Nd2 *

