Qf3 {This attacks c6 and f7 at the same time. Black has to concede something.} 
Ne7 11. Qxf7+ Kd8 {There is no immediate move. Simple castling should be enough 
to kill off black.} 12. O-O Qb4 13. Rfe1 {Re3 followed by Rd3 is a massive 
threat which black can barely stop.} *

