giving the bishop away anyways.} dxc6 5. d3 g6 6. O-O Bg7 7. Nc3 Nf6 8. Be3 
{This is NOT like the mainline because instead of b6 black wasted a tempo on a6. 
And this makes all the difference. Because now e5 cannot be played like it can 
in the mainline. Because c5 is not defended. 8. Be3 e5?! 9. Nxe5 Nxe4 10. Nxe4 
Bxe5 11. Bxc5 Black now has to waste a move playing b6 to play e5.} b6 9. h3 
{Blocks Bg4. e5 is still not possible because if 9. h3 e5 10. Nxe5 Nxe4 11. Qf3! 
wins for white. The king is not castled.} O-O 10. Qd2 *

